# Public genome data staged by fetch_public_data.sh. These bytes are DERIVED
# from real human genomes (1000 Genomes / IGSR) and are NEVER committed — the
# paper's human-data policy is: ship scripts + source pointers + aggregates, not
# genotypes. Reviewers regenerate this cache from the authoritative source with
#   bash docs/paper/experiments/fetch_public_data.sh
*
!.gitignore
